Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.17,*Default,Asu,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:24.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I had nothing prepared, I just let the chocolate melt and then freeze it back into a new shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she will be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:28.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:32.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to give this out already, to my favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:36.51,*Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada Kyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:38.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:43.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:44.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you sleep the entire day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:48.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:02.99,*Default,Opening,0000,0000,0000,,Mother went to heaven the year she gave birth to Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:06.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father left a huge debt after gambling and is now missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:10.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving only the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:13.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place we live in is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a beaten up 40 year old apartment with one room and no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:17.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:20.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:57.35,*Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,A Day of Jealousy, Chocolate, and Valentine's Day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.47,*Default,Kyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Just leave it up to Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:05.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From school to work, that's what Onee-chan says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really tough, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she always keeps up a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:14.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've ever made chocolate for Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:17.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I give this to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:21.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you for everything!" sounds a little strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:27.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3:30, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I should go pick up Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:12.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't come out yet... Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:16.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's left school already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:57.81,*Default,Kyo,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:00.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:08.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, please read the letter inside. I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan... already has someone she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:47.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do with this chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:03.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:11.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry... what's for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:36.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's Onee-chan... it's normal that she has someone she likes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.10,*Default,Kyo,0000,0000,0000,,Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Spacing out like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:46.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:48.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Onee-chan will help you with those.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:55.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I can do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, here, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:03.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:08.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So-sorry. It's fine, I can do this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:10.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan should go get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Asu says so... then okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:44.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can give it to her anymore... my chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:07.17,*Default,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys see the soccer game from yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:08.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:13.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent wasn't that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the person that Onee-chan likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:18.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it, but the other team was a bit cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:23.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of a person he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:27.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As her younger sister, I have to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:38.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu isn't back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahahaha... welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're club activities tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try hard tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has quite a number of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:39.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He helped that grandma carry her suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:43.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he even helped her up the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:48.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... might be a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:55.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, but, but! This isn't enough, I can't hand over my sister just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he let his seat to a pregnant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:03.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he gave the wallet he found to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:07.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he got back the balloon that the kid lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he's giving directions to a lost foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:16.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! That's still not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:19.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't accept him with only these reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must find out his true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:09.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he even recycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:12.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this possible... he's too perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:31.00,*Default,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,(The neighboring town has meat to eat, so the distance doesn't seem too far.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:39.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(We got off two stations early and finally bought meat with the money we saved this month.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.08,*Default,Asu,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder Onee-chan likes him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:02.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... just what am I doing....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:19.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:37.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were acting a little strange since yesterday... I wanted to ask what was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:40.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This chocolate must be the reason, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:42.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, who are you giving this to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't have been... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:49.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan doesn't even want my chocolate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:49.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:53.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday you gave chocolate to a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:54.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw that, Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:13:01.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day... one day... Onee-chan will go to that person's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving me all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:06.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even want my chocolate, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:07.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:16.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:20.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan won't accept my chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:46.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... I can't ever give chocolates to Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she accepts it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:06.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll just say that she's glad to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... she won't be truly happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:17.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... Onee-chan already has someone she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:21.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just an annoying child...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:23.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:40.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I really should cheer Onee-chan on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:44.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:16.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he waiting for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:19.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it's... Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:47.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... did he go off with another girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:48.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:49.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:52.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:15:58.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:59.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:03.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness... so you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tha-thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:07.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:11.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just here... and then... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:12.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, meat buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:19.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw an advertisement that said there will be meat buns for sale at 10 yen each.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:22.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 yen!? Where was this ad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no... I set the price too low.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:28.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, they'll get sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are the advertisements?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:32.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... that... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:33.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. It's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:37.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:44.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it advertised, Asu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:47.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... that... where was it again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:50.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!? No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:56.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to eat them with Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she knew that the one she likes has a girlfriend already,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:02.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan will probably be very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:09.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He's the type of person who accepted the chocolate but went off with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those types of people are better off dumped by Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:20.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Uh... Onee-chan, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:22.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:28.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it! The 10 yen meat buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:32.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It's really 10 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:37.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Onee-chan. You really found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:41.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? You're the one that's amazing, because you found it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:48.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Anyway, let's go in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:52.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they can pass us while we're entering this store than that'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:53.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:58.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... are these meat buns really 10 yen a piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Right now we're having a special promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to buy one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:04.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes, please give me two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:06.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... if she saw a picture of him holding another girl's hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:11.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan will probably not like him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:25.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Onee-chan's sake... What I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:27.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, since it's rare that we've come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:36.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's buy two more, so it's two for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:45.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, the two of you got together fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:52.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I didn't say anything afterwards, I was worried about how it turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:55.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens later, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:16.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave that chocolate as a favor for one of my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:23.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mistook it for something else... how embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, tricking you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:31.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:34.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you become worried later about something like this again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:38.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just remember that Onee-chan will not leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:39.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:45.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:20:00.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Asu was worried about me, so I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha, I'm sorry, you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:11.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:14.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, don't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:18.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bringing that person a warm coat to wear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:25.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then finding cheap meat buns to eat together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:30.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I think that Onee-chan will one day do such things for someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:41.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think when that time comes, Onee-chan will definitely not leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:46.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, even if I answered, "Yes", will that be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:49.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If... that time really comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:52.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:56.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you giving this chocolate to anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:05.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To my favorite person!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:10.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:14.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up! Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is your favorite person?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:21.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... the choice I make... is the one that will bring happiness to favorite Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:23:00.74,*Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,I hear a ghost... a ghost's voice, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:03.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... It's all right Onee-chan, I will be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.06,0:23:05.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Binbou Shimai Monogatari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:08.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Day of Guitars, Dreams and the Music Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:09.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:26.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Omoitei modorenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:26.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we can't return to our memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:31.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kyou wo ikii asuotsukamo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:31.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's seize today and search for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:50.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hitorimo ochimo hitorikiri janai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:50.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be by myself, but I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:59.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Futarimo ochimo futarikimi janai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:59.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's only the two of us, we're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:09.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Soredemokoboreru namida no mae ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:09.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when seeing my tears about to fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:18.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Egao nashi ugokyuu dekiru noka nai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:18.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can I still smile and take a deep breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:23.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Omoitei modorenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:23.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we can't return to our memories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:27.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kyou wo ikii asuotsukamo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:27.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's seize today and search for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:37.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kagega eno naikimi no owoseki wa kokoro ni aru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:37.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That unreachable jewel is there within your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:42.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mukai kaze ni shingokyuu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:42.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face the oncoming wind and take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:50.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ta ainaiosha be iga
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:50.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when everyday talk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:54.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fuinito gi re ta tokimo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:54.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gets interrupted,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:59.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ko oshite sobani iru dakede
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:59.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all I need is you by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:02.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Anshin tekiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:02.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I feel safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:08.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Obekowo ruwa ni na de ru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:08.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind face of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:12.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Soyokaze ni tai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:12.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is just like a gentle wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:16.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gyuto gyuto te to te wo tsunaitara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:16.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We tightly hold each other's hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:21.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sakamichi wo kage a ga ra wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:21.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and run up that hilly path together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.91,0:22:25.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ashita wa zettai tanoshiine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.91,0:22:25.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow will definitely be another happy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:30.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nara n de yuko o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:30.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us walk shoulder to shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:34.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gyuto gyuto kaze wo tsu kama e tara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:34.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tightly hold on to that flowing wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:39.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ryuote hirogeto doketai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:39.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to spread my arms out and give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:43.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gyuto gyuto ashita no asa atemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:43.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We tightly hold each other's hands tomorrow and the day after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.33,0:22:50.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nara n de yuko iisho ni yuko o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.33,0:22:50.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoulder to shoulder, let us walk ahead together.
